  "detailed_description": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2568700/extras/1c963a013ad0cf5db1651c9e8ee3cc2e.webp?t=1772058077\" width=600 height=50 /></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2568700/extras/35420ca20bcb34f80b6a10fbfa9e12be.poster.avif?t=1772058077\" width=600 height=160 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2568700/extras/35420ca20bcb34f80b6a10fbfa9e12be.webm?t=1772058077\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2568700/extras/35420ca20bcb34f80b6a10fbfa9e12be.mp4?t=1772058077\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>Turbo Tails is a silly arcade animal racer. Consume <strong>Food Pickups</strong> littered across the tracks to power up your critter. Unleash your food power as gaseous turbo boost or leave it behind as a gift to mess with your opponents. Turbo Tails features a unique handling mechanic where taking on food increases your weight, in turn reducing your <strong>maneuverability</strong>.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2568700/extras/279bd4f86889da264978893ed0d19b29.webp?t=1772058077\" width=600 height=50 /></span><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2568700/extras/5ec339cda101a11345aae3448a64508a.webp?t=1772058077\" width=600 height=50 /></span> <br>Compete in a <strong>variety of environments</strong>, from twisty trails to muddy meadows. Featuring challenging <strong>track hazards</strong> such as river crossings, slippery fruit trails, wandering machines and more!<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2568700/extras/6ae1678d4cbf33f0e8b9561a4a499ff3.poster.avif?t=1772058077\" width=600 height=160 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2568700/extras/6ae1678d4cbf33f0e8b9561a4a499ff3.webm?t=1772058077\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2568700/extras/6ae1678d4cbf33f0e8b9561a4a499ff3.mp4?t=1772058077\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2568700/extras/279bd4f86889da264978893ed0d19b29.webp?t=1772058077\" width=600 height=50 /></span><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2568700/extras/3d2fd446e62bf821c9fb6b4e1131091d.webp?t=1772058077\" width=600 height=50 /></span><br>Eat food littered around the track to gain <strong>Turbo</strong> boost. The more you eat, the stronger the Turbo! Save up a bunch of food for a long straight and leave the competition behind in a cloud of gas. Use your Turbo boost to create shortcuts or obtain those harder to reach pickups.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2568700/extras/2d8f627abd370a42c6debbc1c8ac4f96.poster.avif?t=1772058077\" width=600 height=160 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2568700/extras/2d8f627abd370a42c6debbc1c8ac4f96.webm?t=1772058077\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2568700/extras/2d8f627abd370a42c6debbc1c8ac4f96.mp4?t=1772058077\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2568700/extras/279bd4f86889da264978893ed0d19b29.webp?t=1772058077\" width=600 height=50 /></span><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2568700/extras/9d6369e4a1bbde1f15f97895f476de53.webp?t=1772058077\" width=600 height=50 /></span><br>Be careful not to consume too much though, as eating will reduce handling. Players will need to be mindful of the track layout when choosing whether to top up on food, else they may find themselves too heavy to make the next turn.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2568700/extras/3a09e30cbaf0452ca67505f8a9b1f832.poster.avif?t=1772058077\" width=600 height=160 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2568700/extras/3a09e30cbaf0452ca67505f8a9b1f832.webm?t=1772058077\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2568700/extras/3a09e30cbaf0452ca67505f8a9b1f832.mp4?t=1772058077\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2568700/extras/279bd4f86889da264978893ed0d19b29.webp?t=1772058077\" width=600 height=50 /></span><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2568700/extras/b0ca6b1772a465990064cfc76044d973.webp?t=1772058077\" width=600 height=50 /></span><br>Alternatively, if you do find yourself overloaded, you may wish to offload all of your food in a pinch to reduce your weight, which can also serve as a nice gift to your opponents, sending them sliding off the track!<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2568700/extras/b0405fc01b4ddc8dd8e9cf113e56843e.poster.avif?t=1772058077\" width=600 height=160 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2568700/extras/b0405fc01b4ddc8dd8e9cf113e56843e.webm?t=1772058077\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2568700/extras/b0405fc01b4ddc8dd8e9cf113e56843e.mp4?t=1772058077\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2568700/extras/279bd4f86889da264978893ed0d19b29.webp?t=1772058077\" width=600 height=50 /></span><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2568700/extras/9678756845ac095fa1611e7ab95699ac.webp?t=1772058077\" width=600 height=50 /></span><br>Choose from a variety of animal athletes, such as <strong>Cow</strong>, <strong>Goat</strong> and who could forget <strong>Sheep</strong>. Don't forget to unlock the special critter and show off to your friends!<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2568700/extras/b250c027a0bbc7b12cfb2d23bf257361.poster.avif?t=1772058077\" width=600 height=160 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2568700/extras/b250c027a0bbc7b12cfb2d23bf257361.webm?t=1772058077\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2568700/extras/b250c027a0bbc7b12cfb2d23bf257361.mp4?t=1772058077\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2568700/extras/279bd4f86889da264978893ed0d19b29.webp?t=1772058077\" width=600 height=50 /></span><br><br><br>Races can be enjoyed in <strong>multiple modes:</strong><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Single Player<br></li><li>4 Player Versus<br></li><li>Online Multiplayer</li></ul>",
